05:27.036 --> 05:29.130
They have robots
that can debone a chicken,

05:29.184 --> 05:32.427
but... a chicken
is not a cow.

05:33.160 --> 05:34.586
No, it is not.

05:34.657 --> 05:37.724
- It's really not even close, yeah.
- Thank you.

05:39.388 --> 05:41.370
Well, Rich,

05:41.529 --> 05:43.880
