05:44.216 --> 05:46.943
so just really good meeting you.

05:47.090 --> 05:48.271
Really good.

05:48.396 --> 05:50.567
But I think we need to be heading back.

05:50.614 --> 05:53.302
I have a class tonight,
and Jack has to work.

05:53.373 --> 05:54.959
But this has just been really nice.

05:55.108 --> 05:56.526
You're leaving?

05:56.919 --> 05:58.708
