06:06.164 --> 06:08.193
Oh, yeah, no, I...

06:08.310 --> 06:10.232
Yeah, yeah,
we can make that work, right?

06:10.497 --> 06:11.802
I'd love it.

06:11.939 --> 06:13.276
Really.

06:15.604 --> 06:16.772
Oh, of course.

06:16.820 --> 06:18.614
Yeah, of course.

06:18.902 --> 06:20.613
I would love it too.

06:25.981 --> 06:28.986
What's a five-letter word
for "redolence"?

06:29.159 --> 06:30.542
