and went grassroots.

07:24.183 --> 07:26.667
- Ah, yes, the small-time.
- Yeah.

07:26.846 --> 07:28.818
Federal government's fucked,

07:29.191 --> 07:31.321
and low expectations is all we got.

07:31.495 --> 07:35.326
Okay, so you're cautiously pessimistic
about the council meeting?

07:35.495 --> 07:36.660
I don't know.

07:36.770 --> 07:38.277
I mean, Beverly Hills did it.

07:38.387 --> 07:40.223
Permanent moratorium,
no more oil drilling.

07:40.367 --> 07:43.862
Yeah, if only we had a better argument
than community health.

07:43.975 --> 07:47.866
Yeah, health does not finance
re-election campaigns.

07:48.649 --> 07:50.612
So you're going to speak at the meeting?

07:52.093 --> 07:53.263
Should I?

07:53.344 --> 07:55.287
Maybe. Isn't that why you took this job?

07:56.917 --> 07:58.795
Well, I took it 'cause you asked.

07:59.748 --> 08:01.753
Well, don't say that.

08:18.440 --> 08:20.546
Hey, can I talk to you?

08:21.105 --> 08:23.066
If we just... if we let it go,

08:23.152 --> 08:24.833
