how much it never happened.

08:24.973 --> 08:27.435
No, don't quote "Mad Men" to me.

08:27.679 --> 08:29.272
And this isn't about you.

08:31.355 --> 08:32.683
Is something wrong with me?

08:32.784 --> 08:34.885
- Yes.
- No, seriously.

08:35.089 --> 08:36.701
I just got turned down for a date.

08:37.145 --> 08:38.741
You really want to know?

08:38.947 --> 08:40.207
Hit me.

08:40.455 --> 08:42.274
You're selfish, man.

08:42.416 --> 08:44.712
Like, epically selfish.

08:44.895 --> 08:47.788
You're like textbook example
of a narcissist.

08:48.019 --> 08:51.469
And you're a man-child.
You're manipulative.

08:51.692 --> 08:53.226
And you want to be good, right?

08:53.423 --> 08:56.157
That ideal appeals to you.
It feels good.

08:56.243 --> 08:58.454
But in practice, it's too much work.

08:58.685 --> 09:00.805
You know what? You should
just play to your strengths.

09:00.927 --> 09:03.423
You got a kind of creepy charm.

09:03.548 --> 09:05.553
