09:10.314 --> 09:12.485
- You're 6 feet tall.
- I'm 6'1".

09:12.562 --> 09:13.814
- Really?
- Yeah.

09:13.930 --> 09:15.380
Oh.

09:16.168 --> 09:18.255
Okay, anything else?

09:18.601 --> 09:20.177
You'll be fine.

09:21.813 --> 09:23.220
- Oh.
- What?

09:23.431 --> 09:24.757
Good news.

09:24.915 --> 09:26.303
I bought some toenail clippers.

09:26.366 --> 09:28.462
I'm going. I'm gone.

09:31.173 --> 09:33.758
So your mom lets you
stay here by yourself?

09:34.110 --> 09:36.445
I mean, I could hang out
at my dad's, but...

09:36.751 --> 09:38.650
Mae-Yi tried giving me dating advice,

09:38.745 --> 09:40.587
and I thought she was kidding,
so I laughed,

09:40.673 --> 09:44.312
but it turns out she was serious,
and now things are strained.

09:44.799 --> 09:46.259
Who's Mae-Yi?

09:46.664 --> 09:49.775
The 23-year-old I walked in
on my dad having sex with.

09:51.735 --> 09:53.496
And you're the one
that had to tell your mom?

09:53.665 --> 09:57.400
After a week of careful deliberation.

09:58.048 --> 09:59.702
Not an easy conversation.

09:59.703 --> 10:01.577
Nope.

10:01.931 --> 10:03.501
And she's still sad.

10:03.837 --> 10:05.814
They both are.

10:06.290 --> 10:07.876
Could have saved a lot in lawyer fees

10:07.939 --> 10:09.807
if they'd just accepted their fate.

10:10.668 --> 10:12.605
You believe in fate?

10:13.532 --> 10:16.762
Well, we're the products
of the people who raised us, right?

10:17.641 --> 10:19.398
My people are fucked.

10:19.576 --> 10:21.017
QED.

10:21.831 --> 10:24.042
In a year, you're gonna leave home

10:24.169 --> 10:26.172
and make so many mistakes

10:26.476 --> 10:28.368
that have nothing to do
with your parents.

10:28.599 --> 10:30.197
So don't fall back on that shit,

10:30.362 --> 10:32.743
'cause it's easy, and it's obvious.

10:49.584 --> 10:50.927
I know.

10:51.642 --> 10:53.418
I'm thinking about it too.

10:53.997 --> 10:58.669
How did the X-Men go backwards
and forwards in time?

10:58.966 --> 11:01.709
Look, that science
is all based on real stuff.

11:01.943 --> 11:03.318
I get the feeling that

11:03.374 --> 11:05.461
first impressions aren't his specialty.

11:05.621 --> 11:08.794
Well, he's a butcher who works at Vons

11:08.842 --> 11:10.762
