through superheroes.

11:10.841 --> 11:12.287
What else is there to say?

11:12.427 --> 11:14.294
Come on. This is exciting.

11:14.498 --> 11:15.640
The Big Tomato.

11:15.688 --> 11:17.227
Oh, well, that's Sacramento.

11:17.275 --> 11:18.332
- Really?
<i>- Yeah.</i>

11:18.380 --> 11:19.702
- We're not in the Big Tomato right now?
<i>- No.</i>

11:19.749 --> 11:21.377
Oh, fuck it, then.

11:21.696 --> 11:23.336
We should bring something
tomorrow, right?

11:23.397 --> 11:25.471
Like a cake or a pie?

11:25.559 --> 11:27.232
Pie. Pie is good.

11:27.662 --> 11:30.101
Yeah, pie's really great.

11:31.452 --> 11:32.966
You okay?

11:34.428 --> 11:37.499
