important enough to say.

12:34.552 --> 12:35.834
That's fine.

12:35.945 --> 12:37.529
You don't have to.

12:39.493 --> 12:41.079
You won't be disappointed?

12:41.229 --> 12:42.709
It's not about me.

12:42.916 --> 12:44.415
It's about you.

12:48.720 --> 12:50.952
You want to sleep here?

13:16.762 --> 13:17.950
- Saya...
- I'm sorry.

13:18.015 --> 13:20.372
